name: jagat embara 2
description: Make a visual design of a 16th century story by presenting the figure of "Bujangga Manik" as an image of spiritual seekers with the aim of going to moksa. trace and mark the name of places and mountains on the island of Java to Bali. From the creation of this work I offer a contemplative meditative impression by considering the arrangement of the balancing space (zen).
